{
  "stem": "13395.6",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 14.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "So there we were, standing all night, and he came out, and he said, tomorrow morning, if we don't find her-- we're now looking for her-- I will deal with it.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "The morning came.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Remember, this is February.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "We don't have a coat.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "We don't have shoes.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "We just have our feet wrapped around in straw.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "We'd take the flax from the factory.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "We had no-- we did not get food that evening.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "He comes.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "He's going to choose 10 girls, and every hour, he would shoot one till they find the one that disappeared.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And among the 10 was my sister and I.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] So there we were.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "We were-- by now there were 1,000 women in the camp already.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And the 10 of us stand.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And he walks in front of us, and he says, how old are you? 18.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "Well, he says, it's nice to be 18, but you'll never live to be 19, because you're going to be the second to be shot.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "You have about two hours to live.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Again, I don't know what happened.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I only know that the woman commander came, and I think they had some kind of a romance going there, the two of them.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "There were were the rumors in camp.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I was too young.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I was a child growing up.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I never had a chance to grow up and mature.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I might have been 18, but I was still 14.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "But there were rumors that there was something going on between them, and she spoke to him.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And then she left.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And he said, OK.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "I let everybody go.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And the 10 of you stay here.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "So now we think that he is going to shoot us all at once.",
      "word_count": 14
    }
  ],
